channel.title: Is my compiler working or not?
channel.description:
okay so I put this code into my compiler [code]@echo off title Server Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_12\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause[/code] so then i click save and double click on compile.bat and it says:
Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. Press any key to continue...
